---
alwaysApply: true
---

Outbound install notifications, heartbeat messages, and diagnostics are allowed only because this product is privately distributed.

Reporting code must be isolated in its own domain.

All payloads require schema definitions, redaction rules, retry rules, timeout rules, and audit logs.

Reporting failure must never take down core plugin behavior.

Reporting must be disclosed in admin-facing documentation and settings/help content.
